                    "subtitle": "Student Reflection",
                    "components": [
                        {
                            "type": "text-paragraph",
                            "text": "We always try to encourage students to reflect on their feelings and their overall situation. It is an important skill which bring to light issues that then the student ca take further steps to solve. In order to do that, we motivate you to read the articles and watch the videos that we consider are very relevant to opening your eyes when it comes to reflection."
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "link-website",
                            "links": [
                                {
                                    "link": "https://www.nursingtimes.net/students/why-are-some-of-us-so-bad-at-caring-for-ourselves/7022596.article?blocktitle=SNT-Editors:&contentID=26823",
                                    "text": "Why are we so bad at caring for ourselves"
                                },
                                {
