                        {
                            "subtitle": "Communicate with yourself – reflect",
                            "type": "text-paragraph",
                            "text": "Various models of reflection are available, there is no “right model”. Students are encouraged to use a model that is right for them, one that they feel can comfortable with. So many of the models use similar language and activities. Reflective models are used to deconstruct events and consolidate learning."
