                {
                    "subtitle": "Looking after yourself",
                    "components": [
                        {
                            "type": "text-paragraph",
                            "text": "Your health is important. If you are not healthy, you will be unable to learn effectively and you may not be able to perform at optimum levels."
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "list-text",
                            "list_elements": [
                                {
                                    "text": "Eat regular meals."
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "Exercise"
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "Take regular breaks ant the appropriate times"
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "Watch that your sleep patterns are healthy, even though you may have to adjust to night shifts or odd shift patterns"
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "Socialise, do your best to stay socially active and do not lose links with friends or family because you are on placement"
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "Take a break if you need it"
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "Contact your tutor or the disability team if you need support"
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "subtitle": "Manging your finances",
                    "components": [
                        {
                            "type": "text-paragraph",
                            "text": "Placements can be a great opportunity to reorganise your finances. You could improve your own financial intelligence. \nConsider what your income may be – what will you earn? Have you saved for placement?\nConsider your outgoings – you may need money for accommodation, transportation, utility."
                        },
